{"questionId":"7690","questionHtml":"<p>Show that at C the temperature is 254 K.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><em><strong>ALTERNATIVE 1:</strong></em></p>\n<p>Since <em>T<sub>B</sub></em> = <em>T<sub>A</sub></em> then <em>T<sub>c</sub></em> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{V_c}{T_B}}}{{{V_B}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>c</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>T</mi>\n          <mi>B</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>B</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> ✔</p>\n<p>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{1.85 \\times 385}}{{2.8}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.85</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>385</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2.8</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> «= 254.4<sup> </sup>K»&nbsp;✔</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>ALTERNATIVE 2:</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{2.80 \\times 1.00}}{{385}} = \\frac{{1.00 \\times 1.85}}{{{T_c}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2.80</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>1.00</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>385</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.00</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>1.85</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>T</mi>\n          <mi>c</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> «K»✔</p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_c} = 385 \\times \\frac{{1.00 \\times 1.85}}{{2.80}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mi>c</mi>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>385</mn>\n  <mo>×</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.00</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mn>1.85</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2.80</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> «= 254.4<sup> </sup>K»&nbsp;✔</p>","meta":{"questionId":"7690","referenceCode":"18N.3.SL.TZ0.7a.ii","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"Show that at C the temperature is 254 K.","paper":"3","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Option B: Engineering physics","Option B: Engineering physics","Option B: Engineering physics (Core topics)","B.2 – Thermodynamics","Option B: Engineering physics","Option B: Engineering physics (Core topics)"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}